 of portfolio margin calculations.\\n\\n**📖 Related Article:** [Portfolio Margin](https://support.deribit.com/hc/en-us/articles/25944756247837-Portfolio-Margin)\\n\\n**Scope:** `account:read`\\n\\n[Try in API console](https://test.deribit.com/api_console?method=%2Fprivate%2Fsimulate_portfolio)\\n\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"og:title\":\"private/simulate_portfolio\",\"keywords\":[\"private/simulate_portfolio\",\"currency\",\"add_positions\",\"simulated_positions\",\"equity\",\"balance\",\"margin_balance\",\"initial_margin\",\"maintenance_margin\",\"projected_initial_margin\",\"projected_maintenance_margin\",\"available_funds\",\"available_withdrawal_funds\",\"available_subaccount_transfer_funds\",\"total_pl\",\"session_rpl\",\"session_upl\",\"futures_pl\",\"futures_session_rpl\",\"futures_session_upl\",\"options_pl\",\"options_session_rpl\",\"options_session_upl\",\"options_value\",\"options_delta\",\"options_gamma\",\"options_theta\",\"options_vega\",\"options_gamma_map\",\"options_theta_map\",\"options_vega_map\",\"delta_total\",\"delta_total_map\",\"projected_delta_total\",\"additional_reserve\",\"spot_reserve\",\"fee_balance\",\"locked_balance\",\"margin_model\",\"portfolio_margining_enabled\",\"cross_collateral_enabled\",\"total_equity_usd\",\"total_initial_margin_usd\",\"total_maintenance_margin_usd\",\"total_margin_balance_usd\",\"total_delta_total_usd\"],\"openapi\":\"/specifications/deribit_upcoming_openapi.json get /private/simulate_portfolio\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/upcoming/account-management/private-simulate_portfolio\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"private/toggle_notifications_from_subaccount\",\"description\":\"Enables or disables email and other notifications for a subaccount. When notifications are disabled, the subaccount will not receive email alerts, trade confirmations, or other notification messages.\\n\\nThis setting only affects notifications sent to the subaccount's email address. Notifications sent to the main account are not affected.\\n\\n**[TFA required](https://docs.deribit.com/articles/security-keys)**\\n\\n**📖 Related Article:** [Managing Subaccounts](https://docs.deribit.com/articles/managing-subaccounts-api)\\n\\n**Scope:** `account:read_write`\\n\\n[Try in API console](https://test.deribit.com/api_console?method=%2Fprivate%2Ftoggle_notifications_from_subaccount)\\n\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"og:title\":\"private/toggle_notifications_from_subaccount\",\"keywords\":[\"private/toggle_notifications_from_subaccount\",\"sid\",\"state\"],\"openapi\":\"/specifications/deribit_upcoming_openapi.json get /private/toggle_notifications_from_subaccount\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/upcoming/account-management/private-toggle_notifications_from_subaccount\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"private/toggle_subaccount_login\",\"description\":\"Enables or disables direct login access for a subaccount. When login is disabled, the subaccount cannot be accessed directly using email and password authentication, but can still be accessed through the main account.\\n\\nIf login is disabled while an active session exists for the subaccount, that session will be immediately terminated.\\n\\n**[TFA required](https://docs.deribit.com/articles/security-keys)**\\n\\n**📖 Related Article:** [Managing Subaccounts](https://docs.deribit.com/articles/managing-subaccounts-api)\\n\\n**Scope:** `account:read_write`\\n\\n[Try in API console](https://test.deribit.com/api_console?method=%2Fprivate%2Ftoggle_subaccount_login)\\n\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"og:title\":\"private/toggle_subaccount_login\",\"keywords\":[\"private/toggle_subaccount_login\",\"sid\",\"state\"],\"openapi\":\"/specifications/deribit_upcoming_openapi.json get /private/toggle_subaccount_login\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/upcoming/account-management/private-toggle_subaccount_login\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"public/get_announcements\",\"description\":\"Retrieves platform