ethod is useful for analyzing historical settlement prices and understanding how contracts have been settled over time.\\n\\n[Try in API console](https://test.deribit.com/api_console?method=%2Fpublic%2Fget_delivery_prices)\\n\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"og:title\":\"public/get_delivery_prices\",\"keywords\":[\"public/get_delivery_prices\",\"index_name\",\"offset\",\"count\",\"records_total\",\"data\",\"date\",\"delivery_price\"],\"openapi\":\"/specifications/deribit_upcoming_openapi.json get /public/get_delivery_prices\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/upcoming/market-data/public-get_delivery_prices\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"public/get_expirations\",\"description\":\"Retrieves all available expiration timestamps for instruments. This method can be used to discover which expiration dates are available for trading, which is useful for finding instruments with specific expiration dates.\\n\\nResults can be filtered by settlement currency, instrument kind (future or option), and currency pair. The response includes expiration timestamps in milliseconds since the UNIX epoch.\\n\\n[Try in API console](https://test.deribit.com/api_console?method=%2Fpublic%2Fget_expirations)\\n\\n\",\"deprecated\":null,\"version\":null,\"og:title\":\"public/get_expirations\",\"keywords\":[\"public/get_expirations\",\"currency\",\"kind\",\"currency_pair\"],\"openapi\":\"/specifications/deribit_upcoming_openapi.json get /public/get_expirations\",\"href\":\"/api-reference/upcoming/market-data/public-get_expirations\",\"autogeneratedByOpenApi\":true},{\"title\":\"public/get_funding_chart_data\",\"description\":\"Retrieves funding rate chart data points for a PERPETUAL instrument within a given time period. The data is formatted for use in charting applications and includes funding rate values at regular intervals.\\n\\nUse the `length` parameter to specify the time period for which to retrieve chart data. This method is useful for visualizing funding rate trends 